@page "/accomplishments"

<PageTitle>Accomplishments &mdash; Devon VanNote</PageTitle>

<section class="section-container">
    <h2 class="section-title">Accomplishments</h2>

    <div class="accomplishments-grid">

        <div class="accomplishment-card">
            <div class="ac-icon">&#127942;</div>
            <div class="ac-body">
                <h3>ADTRAV Family Values Award 2024</h3>
                <p>
                    Awarded in January 2025 for upholding a workplace culture where everyone is treated with dignity
                    and respect, striving to exceed client needs, setting a high standard of work, and embracing
                    innovation by seizing opportunities to expand, transform, and elevate new and existing solutions.
                </p>
                <div class="ac-tags">
                    <span class="skill-badge secondary">Leadership</span>
                    <span class="skill-badge secondary">Culture</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accomplishment-card">
            <div class="ac-icon">&#128200;</div>
            <div class="ac-body">
                <h3>Team Happiness Score 8&nbsp;/&nbsp;10</h3>
                <p>
                    Maintained a sprint team happiness score average of 8 out of 10 while leading a team of
                    senior software engineers &mdash; reflecting a consistent focus on psychological safety,
                    clear communication, and team growth.
                </p>
                <div class="ac-tags">
                    <span class="skill-badge secondary">Team Leadership</span>
                    <span class="skill-badge secondary">Agile</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accomplishment-card">
            <div class="ac-icon">&#9729;</div>
            <div class="ac-body">
                <h3>Azure App Configuration Library</h3>
                <p>
                    Architected a .NET 8 C# class library with an extension method that allows a Web Application
                    to register with Azure App Configuration using Event Subscriptions paired with Azure Service Bus
                    to push cloud config updates to the application at runtime. Creates and deletes Azure Service Bus
                    subscriptions on startup and shutdown &mdash; all via a single line of code on
                    <code>WebApplicationBuilder</code> in <code>Program.cs</code>.
                </p>
                <div class="ac-tags">
                    <span class="skill-badge">.NET 8</span>
                    <span class="skill-badge">Azure App Configuration</span>
                    <span class="skill-badge">Azure Service Bus</span>
                    <span class="skill-badge">C#</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accomplishment-card">
            <div class="ac-icon">&#128274;</div>
            <div class="ac-body">
                <h3>One-Time Password System</h3>
                <p>
                    Developed a 6-character alphanumeric OTP system that integrates with an existing legacy
                    Identity Server. Leverages Azure Functions and Azure Service Bus to handle code generation
                    and delivery. New code built with .NET 8 and Blazor.
                </p>
                <div class="ac-tags">
                    <span class="skill-badge">.NET 8</span>
                    <span class="skill-badge">Blazor</span>
                    <span class="skill-badge">Azure Functions</span>
                    <span class="skill-badge">Azure Service Bus</span>
                    <span class="skill-badge">Identity Server</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accomplishment-card">
            <div class="ac-icon">&#128736;</div>
            <div class="ac-body">
                <h3>Visual Studio API Template</h3>
                <p>
                    Created a Visual Studio project template for new .NET 8 API projects that spins up an API
                    pre-configured with Identity token / client credential authentication, a company-styled
                    Swagger page, an integration test project, a unit test project, a data layer, service
                    layer, and presentation layer &mdash; significantly accelerating new API development.
                </p>
                <div class="ac-tags">
                    <span class="skill-badge">.NET 8</span>
                    <span class="skill-badge">Visual Studio</span>
                    <span class="skill-badge">Swagger</span>
                    <span class="skill-badge">Identity</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accomplishment-card">
            <div class="ac-icon">&#127918;</div>
            <div class="ac-body">
                <h3>Petrified &mdash; 2D Asymmetrical Game</h3>
                <p>
                    Helped develop UI, audio, music, voice&nbsp;/&nbsp;text chat, and gameplay features for a 2D
                    asymmetrical game in Unity. UI includes all menus and in-game interfaces integrated with
                    Vivox &amp; Photon for player communication, an event log, and Steam friends list &mdash;
                    all Steam Deck Verified. Created a powerup that flips the camera (reversing controls) and
                    reverses audio for 10 seconds.
                </p>
                <div class="ac-tags">
                    <span class="skill-badge">Unity</span>
                    <span class="skill-badge">C#</span>
                    <span class="skill-badge">Vivox</span>
                    <span class="skill-badge">Photon</span>
                    <span class="skill-badge">Steam</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>
